Karbonn Titanium S3 (Black)

Extremely budget friendly, loaded with latest features and an easy-to-use device, Karbonn Titanium S3 smartphone gives you true value for your money. It has a large 5 inch quarter HD display with a wide view angle that enhances your video viewing experience. You can capture amazing photographs with its 8 MP auto focus rear camera with flash. The 2 megapixel camera allows you to take beautiful selfies. You can easily do multi-tasking on this smart mobile phone as it incorporates 1.3 GHz quad-core processor with 512 MB RAM. Having Android 4.4 KitKat operating system, it lets you download thousands of entertaining and useful applications. You can store large amount of media files in the 4 GB memory of this Karbonn phone which can be further expanded up to 32 GB. You can buy this pocket-friendly device from Snapdeal.com with 1 year warranty at lowest possible price. 

5 Inch qHD Capacitive Touchscreen

This smart device by Karbonn incorporates a large 5 inch capacitive touchscreen. It renders beautiful colours and contrast to images that enhances your viewing experience. Its wide view angle enables you to share information with various groups at once. You can open multiple apps simultaneously on Karbonn Titanium S3 and still navigate smoothly without facing any delay in response time.

8 Megapixel Auto Focus Primary Camera with Flash

Karbonn Titanium S3 smartphone incorporates 8 megapixel auto focus camera that captures amazing shots. It has Face Detection and Smile Detection feature that never lets a smile slip away from your frame. With its multi-angle shot and motion-track, you can click stable images when the subject is moving. It also features Panorama function that stiches a wider scenery into a single image. You can also use the rear camera for recording videos on this smartphone. It comes with flash light that helps you to click beautiful shots even in low light conditions. 

2 Megapixel Front Camera

Taking selfies have now become more fun. With the 2 megapixel front camera of this Karbonn Titanium smartphone you can click clear and sharp images with your friends. It captures more background area thus adding richness to the frame.

 

 1.3 GHz Quad Core Processor

This Karbonn smartphone delivers brilliant processing performance. It is equipped with a powerful 1.3 GHz quad-core processor that provides responsive functioning to the device. You can also play graphic intensive video games on this smartphone easily.

Android 4.4 KitKat OS with 512 MB RAM

Equipped with Android 4.4 KitKat operating system, this device allows you to download thousands of apps to make everyday life more enjoyable and fun. 512 MB RAM makes this smartphone super swift and super-smooth in functioning. You can work and play simultaneously on this Titanium S3 device without facing any time lag issues.

4 GB Internal Memory Expandable up to 32 GB

You can keep important documents always handy with you in a safe way on Karbonn Titanium S3 smartphone. This phone has 4 GB internal memory which can be expanded up to 32 GB using a micro SD card. It also allows you to store images, videos and other multi-media information for instant access anytime & anywhere.

1800 mAh Battery

Equipped with 1800 mAh battery, this Karbonn phone provides you long hours of talk time. You can watch videos, play music and surf internet on this device without worrying about the battery draining out. With Karbonn Titanium S3, you get non-stop entertainment on-the-go.

1 Year Karbonn India Warranty

Buy Karbonn Titanium S3 smartphone from Snapdeal.com and get 1 year free warranty on the product. You can contact any Karbonn authorized service centre across India if a problem occurs in the device. This warranty stands against manufacturing defects and you can get free services for a year from its date of purchase.
